xt "100200,69200,116100,80200"
st "
This transition from rt1REP_B purpose is to capture DataSync following thee expected number of words (BC sends more words than indicated in command). However, when the bus goes Idle from the BC side to let the RT send the status, the tail-off of the signaln on badly terminated busses may trigger this transition. This is more likely to occur than a BC sending to many words, so it is debatable wheter this transition should rather be removed.
"
